                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.U.34.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 22a</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00">undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>In connection with reparation and restitution, the States entitled to reparations
                    will be represented in Hungary by Reparation and Restitution Delegations. The
                    personnel of these Delegations will enjoy diplomatic status and the maintenance
                    costs of such Delegations will be borne by the Hungarian Government.</p>
            </div>
